Class LibraryStaff

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
      • LibraryStaff
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SystemUsers

    public class LibraryStaff
extends Person
    Class that represents a library staff. It has methods like searching, adding and removing books also adding a new user. Otherwise another method check the staff's password to login the system.
